1
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,040
Come in.

2
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,140
I've been waiting for you.

3
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:25,280
When did you discover me?

4
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:29,440
When I compared all the fingerprints from Lienü Cliff

5
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,720
and found nothing,

6
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,320
I suspected

7
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:35,000
that there must be another person hiding.

8
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,860
And that night,

9
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,650
I was absolutely not mistaken.

10
00:01:37,759 --> 00:01:38,640
So the murderer

11
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,120
is the person who seems to have no limbs.

12
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,120
The night I checked in

13
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:47,640
and the night the female official had the accident,

14
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,570
Qiuyue and I both lost track of you.

15
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,600
You used your height to hide.

16
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,320
What is it?

17
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:58,080
You must have used this to cover up

18
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,320
and kill Madam Gu and the militia.

19
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:03,840
And the round bloodstains left at the scene

20
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,440
were left by the stilts on your feet.

21
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,919
They deserved to die.

22
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:11,160
It's a pity you ruined it.

23
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,100
Otherwise,

24
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,280
I would have avenged everything.

25
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,920
But I guess

26
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,760
you're not taking revenge for yourself,

27
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,820
but for the owner of an empty grave in the back mountain.

28
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,880
Right.

29
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,040
Yinlian was killed by them.

30
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,820
Because of my illness,

31
00:02:29,079 --> 00:02:30,200
I am short

32
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:31,440
and look like a child.

33
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,120
I have suffered all kinds of bullying.

34
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:33,720
Take it out.

35
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,280
It was Yinlian who helped me.

36
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:35,720
Give me money.

37
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,640
Dwarfism.

38
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,000
Go away.

39
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:38,800
What?

40
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:45,920
You're such a small child,

41
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,530
where are your parents?

42
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,800
If you are willing,

43
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,800
I will be your sister from now on.

44
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:52,840
Really?

45
00:02:53,160 --> 00:02:53,760
Really.

46
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:57,560
Her husband just died,

47
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,660
and her parents-in-law sent her to Lienv Cliff.

48
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,160
They said it was to preserve her chastity for her husband.

49
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:04,920
Actually,

50
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:08,380
they were afraid she would divide the family property.

51
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,960
I found out where Lienv Cliff was.

52
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,720
I begged all the way

53
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,920
just to see Yinlian.

54
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:19,720
Unexpectedly, when passing by the back mountain,

55
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:42,920
Go.

56
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,080
Yinlian.

57
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,520
Yinlian.

58
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,440
Yinlian, wake up.

59
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,600
Yinlian.

60
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:14,280
Yinlian had her tongue cut out.

61
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:17,339
Her limbs were broken, and she barely looked human.

62
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:19,680
She didn't

63
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:22,360
even get to look at me

64
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,560
before she died.

65
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,480
So you hid at Lienu Cliff

66
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,920
to find out the truth.

67
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,120
Heavens be praised.

68
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,640
I found out

69
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:33,760
they were the ones who killed Yinlian.

70
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:35,020
How could I let them go?

71
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,680
This time,

72
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:39,120
we need to find someone docile and obedient.

73
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,920
Don't let it be like the last one,

74
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,520
who woke up crying and screaming,

75
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,520
refusing to obey.

76
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,720
After the buyer beat her to death,

77
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,580
we had to help dispose of the body.

78
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,320
Be careful.

79
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:52,159
Don't let the secret out.

80
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,880
It's not like they don't know

81
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,320
where those women came from.

82
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,360
If things get out of hand,

83
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,490
they are guilty too.

84
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,440
And you,

85
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,320
you too.

86
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,080
Next time, use a stronger dose.

87
00:05:03,080 --> 00:05:05,540
Just make sure she doesn't wake up on the way.

88
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,760
Don't worry, my lord.

89
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:11,080
Leave it all to me.

90
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,840
Then remember not to overdo it.

91
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,080
If she dies,

92
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,720
we won't get paid either.

93
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,240
Drink, my lord, drink.

94
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:27,200
Come, drink.

95
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:35,020
I get annoyed just looking at you.

96
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:38,400
Stop lingering around me.

97
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,920
Don't delay me from making a fortune.

98
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,780
I'll deal with you when I get back.

99
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:39,820
This is the murder weapon, right?

100
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,400
You're quite inventive.

101
00:06:43,080 --> 00:06:44,280
She deserved to die.

102
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,040
Not only did she traffic

103
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,240
those women including Yin Lian,

104
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,320
she also abused her daughter-in-law Gu Yu.

105
00:06:50,320 --> 00:06:51,450
She's barely human.

106
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,280
As for the militia,

107
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,280
She deserves to die too.

108
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:01,640
Your mother-in-law has saved up a lot of money over the years.

109
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,760
She's dead,

110
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,160
but the money is still here.

111
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:04,680
Speak.

112
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,440
Where did she hide the money?

113
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:29,200
No wonder your mother-in-law called you a bitch.

114
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,720
If you don't tell the truth,

115
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,650
I'll send you to the back mountain.

116
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,960
It's the Holy Maiden!

117
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,160
Holy Maiden.

118
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,520
Then why did you kill Sister Gu?

119
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,680
She is innocent.

120
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,720
She is so pitiful.

121
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,880
She didn't kill Gu Yu.

122
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,560
The method those people use

123
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,520
to traffic women is to fake their deaths.

124
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:18,720
The way is to make them

125
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:21,380
take a kind of psychoactive anesthetic.

126
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,640
And a small amount of this potion

127
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,200
can cause hallucinations,

128
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:27,480
with symptoms just like the female official that night.

129
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,410
So you also used this stolen potion

130
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:32,780
to let Mrs. Gu and the militia suffer the consequences.

131
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,720
But once the dose of this potion is increased,

132
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,920
it will cause the user

133
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:52,080
to experience symptoms of suspended animation.

134
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,720
However,

135
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,640
if they are not awakened

136
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,280
within a certain period of time,

137
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,240
the user

138
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,560
will really die.

139
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,520
So

140
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:03,180
you took advantage of this

141
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,530
to wait for me to show up.

142
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,160
But

143
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,600
what if I didn't come?

144
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,960
A person who can risk everything

145
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,960
to avenge a friend

146
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,120
must surely

147
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,240
not be

148
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,760
a heinous villain.

149
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:19,920
The reason you put Gu Yu into suspended animation

150
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,800
is that you wanted to use the same method

151
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,000
to get her out of here.

152
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,120
So it's impossible for you not to come.

153
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,920
As for you taking Miss Chai hostage,

154
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,320
you also wanted to use her

155
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,600
to exchange for Gu Yu from me,

156
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,200
right?

157
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,000
Gu Yu is really too pitiful.

158
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,000
The day you came,

159
00:09:36,280 --> 00:09:37,920
I felt you were not simple.

160
00:09:38,920 --> 00:09:40,480
That's why I peeked.

161
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:41,760
Sure enough.

162
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,520
My only regret

163
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:45,880
is that I couldn't finish all this.

164
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:48,680
Sorry,

165
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:49,760
Yinlian.

166
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,650
Xiaohua, don't!

167
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,370
Sister Chai,

168
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,960
you are a good person.

169
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,320
You know what?

170
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,880
Since I came to this wretched place,

171
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,560
I have never seen Gu Yu

172
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:03,040
and everyone as happy as that day.

173
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,720
And what you said here last night,

174
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,920
I saw it all.

175
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:09,920
Xiaohua, stop!

176
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,520
This medicine can make a person feign death,

177
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:19,360
but there's a chance they might never wake up.

178
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,320
I would never make

179
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,980
such a high-risk investment.

180
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:25,180
Since I became a widow, my mother-in-law

181
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,920
has been controlling me,

182
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,360
abusing me,

183
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,800
and forcing me to remain a widow.

184
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,040
If she was slightly displeased,

185
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,500
she would beat me for days.

186
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,200
I had to make paper crafts day and night.

187
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,380
Xiaohua seeking revenge against her

188
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,720
also saved me.

189
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,160
Sister Guyu,

190
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,320
Sister Chai,

191
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,800
and Yinlian.

192
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,640
You are all the best women in the world.

193
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,720
Why are your lives so bitter?

194
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,400
Especially Yinlian,

195
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,720
who died so tragically.

196
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,240
Every night, I can see

197
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,640
how she died in front of me.

198
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,680
Perhaps Yinlian

199
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,660
was just an inconspicuous speck of dust.

200
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:15,010
But you've seen her at her most beautiful.

201
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:16,320
Why don't

202
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:17,520
you describe it to me,

203
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:18,850
and I'll draw it for you.

204
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,940
Since everything is settled,

205
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:42,080
why don't they leave?

206
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:44,920
This is their own choice.

207
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:47,760
This place may be a prison,

208
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,160
but the outside world

209
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,720
is also a cage to them.

210
00:11:51,920 --> 00:11:53,440
If they follow their hearts

211
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,440
and make a choice,

212
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:55,890
maybe this place

213
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,530
will become a paradise.

214
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:15,290
This is what I promised you.

215
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,980
I didn't break my word.

216
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:18,680
Remember.

217
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,250
You must live a beautiful life.

218
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,960
Don't let me down.

219
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,240
Yinlian.

220
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,620
Maybe in the next life,

221
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,720
we will meet again.

222
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,360
By then,

223
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,960
I will continue to guard you,

224
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:49,340
and I won't let you get hurt again.

225
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,640
It's all settled.

226
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:09,170
So you knew it all along.

227
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:15,210
You two really are on the same wavelength.

228
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,170
Where are you going?

229
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,920
Since the case is closed,

230
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:21,880
of course I'm going to arrest the murderer.

231
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,010
I forgot to tell you.

232
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:26,200
The murderer jumped off a cliff to escape punishment.

233
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:32,120
Don't look.

234
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,560
He was smashed into a meat patty.

235
00:13:33,560 --> 00:13:34,360
Speaking of meat patties,

236
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,200
I haven't had breakfast yet.

237
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,400
The boss is treating!

238
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,600
Liu Chuan is so talented.

239
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:07,720
It would be a pity to let his talents go to waste.

240
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:10,280
It seems I must give him a chance to be valued by the court

241
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:11,720
and show his skills,

242
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,520
so he can work for me.
